<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Message Received - XIANZE 2026</title>
</head>

<body
    style="margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; background-color: #f8f5ff;">
    <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"
        style="background-color: #f8f5ff; padding: 40px 20px;">
        <tr>
            <td align="center">
                <table role="presentation" width="600" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"
                    style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff 0%, #f0e8ff 100%); border-radius: 24px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(109, 64, 212, 0.15);">

                    <!-- Header -->
                    <tr>
                        <td
                            style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6D40D4 0%, #9333EA 100%); padding: 40px 40px 30px; text-align: center;">
                            <h1
                                style="margin: 0; color: #ffffff; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.5px;">
                                ✨ XIANZE 2026
                            </h1>
                            <p style="margin: 10px 0 0; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); font-size: 14px;">
                                Inter-College Technical Symposium
                            </p>
                        </td>
                    </tr>

                    <!-- Content -->
                    <tr>
                        <td style="padding: 50px 40px;">
                            <h2 style="margin: 0 0 20px; color: #1a1a2e; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 600;">
                                Hi {{name}}! 👋
                            </h2>

                            <p style="margin: 0 0 25px; color: #4a4a6a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7;">
                                We've received your message and our team will get back to you shortly.
                            </p>

                            <div
                                style="background: rgba(109, 64, 212, 0.08); border-left: 4px solid #6D40D4; border-radius: 0 12px 12px 0; padding: 20px 24px; margin: 30px 0;">
                                <p style="margin: 0; color: #6D40D4; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600;">
                                    💬 What happens next?
                                </p>
                                <p style="margin: 10px 0 0; color: #4a4a6a; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;">
                                    Our team typically responds within 24 hours. In the meantime, feel free to explore
                                    our exciting events!
                                </p>
                            </div>

                            <!-- CTA Button -->
                            <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="margin: 35px 0;">
                                <tr>
                                    <td
                                        style="border-radius: 12px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6D40D4 0%, #9333EA 100%);">
                                        <a href="https://xianze.tech/events" target="_blank"
                                            style="display: inline-block; padding: 16px 32px; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600;">
                                            Browse Events →
                                        </a>
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                            </table>

                            <p style="margin: 0; color: #6a6a8a; font-size: 14px;">
                                Best regards,<br>
                                <strong style="color: #1a1a2e;">The XIANZE Team</strong>
                            </p>
                        </td>
                    </tr>

                    <!-- Footer -->
                    <tr>
                        <td style="background: #1a1a2e; padding: 30px 40px; text-align: center;">
                            <p style="margin: 0 0 10px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); font-size: 13px;">
                                KGCAS · School of Computational Sciences
                            </p>
                            <p style="margin: 0; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); font-size: 12px;">
                                © 2026 XIANZE. All rights reserved.
                            </p>
                        </td>
                    </tr>

                </table>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</body>

</html>